nde2.methodcalls.discovery

Class GetAreaParentMethodCall

  • java.lang.Object
    • nde2.methodcalls.BaseMethodCall
      • nde2.methodcalls.discovery.BaseMethodCall
        • nde2.methodcalls.discovery.GetAreaParentMethodCall

  • public class GetAreaParentMethodCall
extends BaseMethodCall
    Encapsulates the GetAreaComparators() method call and returns the closest comparator. Creation follows the Builder pattern, sort of.

    This operation gives you the higher level areas which contain your chosen area, which are considered useful for comparison purposes. For example, the comparator areas of an Output Area might be the local authority, the region (if within England) and the country.

    Author:
    filip
